    "title": "Opening for Production Engineer at Astral Pipes",
    "description": "Astral Pipes has an exciting opening for a Production Engineer at our Mysuru office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Astral Pipes:\nAstral Pipes is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in 5S\n• Proficiency in FMEA\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mysuru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Astral Pipes!",
